Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨厌的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该听那个故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个发生在似乎即将下雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闷热阴天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这天遭到杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和深爱的男人\N幽会时的暗号遭到利用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨遭因嫉妒而发狂的妻子杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍徘徊在那间公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在闷热的阴天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就会发出那个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人以前所用的幽会暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将房间的电灯关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待着新的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，確認
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是指这间公寓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将房间的电灯开了又关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是有妇之夫和爱人幽会的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她像往常一般进了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里等待着她的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却是手持菜刀的男人的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个发生在似乎即将下雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闷热阴天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这天遭到杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人为了找男人求救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命朝门口爬去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却在门前力气用尽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人也没有来接她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人也被男人背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽会时的暗号遭到利用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨遭妻子杀害的女人怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍徘徊在那间公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跟她遇害当天\N同样的闷热阴天里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就会发出那个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人以前所用的幽会暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将房间的电灯关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里等待着新的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在 G 公寓的104号房里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个网站以讨论谣传为主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方即使没有荧幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电脑也会用简单易懂的方式\N念给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己来问我网路的事的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在稔他家听到的故事一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天是阴天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一楼的空房间灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去澡堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这么闷热的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在玩什么奇怪的游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打开罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，这个人好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,104号房的鬼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个网站我也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是常听到的恐怖故事而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你也是这么想的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我刚刚看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一楼角落的房间电灯在闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且故事里提到的 G 公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也叫作“ GAB 城崎”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一楼角落的房间又没人住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有在闪烁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你胆子这么小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你睡这里好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是男生的房间睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就好，今天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会对你做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了还得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经天亮了，竟然还睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳突然是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好怕的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我要出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以出去乱跑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这果然就是那个鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以靠近那个房间喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去问问看管理员好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过要怎么开口问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道要问她\N“这间公寓被诅咒了吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就已经迟交房租了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说这个感觉就像是故意在找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,云层很厚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，完全没什么奇怪的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道真是我想太多了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是身边老是发生那种事\N谁还受得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是公寓名称里有个“ G ”字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是 GonzaIez\N或是 GaI & Do 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,况且那个故事巧合实在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么门打开\N就有女人拿着菜刀站着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说这种奇怪的故事\N我才觉得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么诅咒报应之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己都这个年纪了\N总觉得很丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会怕黑色的动物之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如说乌鸦、黑猫\N还有蝙蝠之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还觉得有点恐怖不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定只是装作毫不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实心里怕得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你根本不需要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是吓了一跳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用那么担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次去看电影的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟学长说就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说你可能是有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用放在心上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你方便的话，下次再一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请振作点，学长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算被吓到也要有个程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什么鬼不鬼故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我背一个男人回家\N你好歹也要替我想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我刚才会晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟鬼故事没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,况且你仔细想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这栋公寓根本没有104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为一楼只有三个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从大门向左边算去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是管理员住的101号房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后右边有两间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样算来，那104号房在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了的话，就忘了那个故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不会痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，你害怕那个房间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没有，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ去確認看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这栋公寓根本没有104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个故事根本就不成立
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一楼有三个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷住的101号室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下两间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,102
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有103
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是空房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停电了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来很近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经快要中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神到补习班去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你万事如意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，對不起把妳吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？我要去补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，请用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香草的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是学长你说如果方便的话\N下次再一起出来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才带我来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了，天气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想坐那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔玩这个也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，我很喜欢玩这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从树木之间射出的阳光真美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起了老家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过去还有更美的地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一栋古老的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从一楼的窗户可以看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电灯在闪烁着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里发呆很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老师，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没有，没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也对，你没必要跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只是补习班的老师而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛，走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有事想跟本须和说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师，这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人单独去不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去一间很棒的店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想说\N一定要带本须和来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师，不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原来是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说梦话说得还真大声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗把脸再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是三楼耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后我根本睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管睡着或醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑里都一直想着104号房的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来病得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去驱鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是说\N是我造成本须和精神衰竭的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果弄清楚那个故事的来源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说应该可以\N让这家伙安心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想找来源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路上流传的鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎都是不可信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是104号房？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界上的确存在着\N无数的谜团和怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过大部分都是自己看错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属于自然现象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过我的确听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地板上爬的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有流出来的黑血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的“亲眼看到”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候是最不可信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人在潜意识中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就能看到\N自己想看或是想相信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那间不应该有的104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个鬼故事\N说的果然就是 GAB 城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去 GAB 城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来，似乎还真有那种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要那种气氛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么偏偏又是这种天气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是灵异现象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是调查的好时机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题的是哪一间？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从大门看去\N左边是管理员住的101号房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后右边有两间空房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和看到电灯闪烁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是里面的角落房间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问一下，那时候本须和是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只…只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保有看过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉也没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么看错的可能性越来越…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，怕那个声音吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去确认看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里守着\N看看有没有人跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是低级的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被我找到\N我就把你抓起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保少爷好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去上面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身体动不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快动，快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仓库？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近东西容易发霉潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想来个大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是电灯泡快要坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直没办法打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了换灯泡\N我找来了各种东西垫脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会叫我来帮忙换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是从门下面\N流出的黑色液体…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搬桌子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我有上去找本须和帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看起来好像很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电灯泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么会有104号房？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来一楼本来有四间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁是103号房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我搬来时做了一点改装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺的是102号房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被搞得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不害怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在营造什么气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到最恐怖的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到ちぃ可能被附身時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是我最恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好什么事都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是蔚蓝的天空最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，还要睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台 DVD 播放机是\N可以玩游戏的优秀机种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然也能以高画质播放各种影像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树的脸好红
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戏吧，玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.09,0:24:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车站前的电器行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,软件八折大降价
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树脸又红了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戏，玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五片一套，一万元日币
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，好料的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.23,0:24:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，好料的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，玩遊戲」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空姐、护士、已婚妇女…

